{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"35e37173-43fd-4f23-88a8-4367b6e96ca5","content":"You're on MSTest 3.8.2 / .NET 9 — great, constructor injection for `TestContext` is fully supported. Here's the recommended pattern:\n\n```csharp\n[TestClass]\npublic class MyTests\n{\n    private readonly TestContext _testContext;\n\n    // Constructor injection for TestContext (MSTest v3+)\n    public MyTests(TestContext testContext)\n    {\n        _testContext = testContext;\n        // Sync-only setup here (runs before each test)\n    }\n\n    [TestInitialize]\n    public async Task SetupAsync()\n    {\n        // Async per-test initialization goes here\n        await SomeAsyncSetup();\n    }\n\n    [TestMethod]\n    public void SyncTest()\n    {\n        _testContext.WriteLine(\"Running sync test\");\n        Assert.IsTrue(true);\n    }\n\n    [TestMethod]\n    public async Task AsyncTest()\n    {\n        await Task.Delay(10);\n        Assert.IsNotNull(_testContext);\n    }\n}\n```\n\n**Key points:**\n\n- **Constructor** — inject `TestContext`, do sync-only setup. Runs before each test.\n- **`[TestInitialize]`** — can return `Task` for async setup. Also runs before each test, after the constructor.\n- **`[ClassInitialize]`** / **`[ClassCleanup]`** — use `static async Task` variants for one-time class-level async setup/teardown.\n- Avoid the legacy `public TestContext TestContext { get; set; }` property pattern — constructor injection is the modern replacement.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"ab785216-1f26-41b1-8f07-cadaf1a05de6","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is on MSTest 3.8.2 with .NET 9. Let me provide the recommended pattern for modern MSTest.\n\nIn MSTest v3+, `TestContext` can be injected via constructor. The recommended pattern for both sync and async initialization is:\n\n1. Constructor injection for `TestContext`\n2. `[TestInitialize]` for per-test sync setup\n3. `[TestInitialize]` can be async (return `Task`) for async setup\n\nLet me provide a clear, concise answer.","outputTokens":517,"requestId":"A02B:1007E7:637F5E8:6C0DD24:6A034CDA"},"id":"2a9b9d2e-bfe8-4c45-a10c-0c84c48abf51","timestamp":"2026-05-12T15:53:10.623Z","parentId":"89d2d8a3-e44a-485f-96a9-56c9b835fd67"}
